text: Veterans Memorial High School is a public high school in Brownsville, Texas (USA). It is one of six high schools operated by the Brownsville Independent School District and classified as a 5a school by the UIL. In 2015, the school was rated "Met Standard" by the Texas Education Agency. ==Athletics== Younger brother to Mission Veterans Memorial patriots.
